            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1688113199321-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based<strong> hob-safe oven-proof casserole dish</strong> with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>duck fat </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Tip: Make sure your dish is oven-proof and safe to use on the hob. Don't have one? Start cooking in a large, wide-based pan then transfer to an oven-proof dish and cover tightly with foil!</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>diced onion</strong> and<strong> diced carrot</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until beginning to soften</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
