    {
      "instruction": "<p>After an initial 25 min, remove the dish from the oven and top with the <strong>cheesy breadcrumbs</strong></p><p>Return the dish to the oven, along with the <strong>spring green parcel<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Cook both for a final 10-12 min or until the duck is golden and crisp and the spring greens are tender – this is your <strong>duck cassoulet &</strong> <strong>buttery spring greens</strong></p><p>Discard the<strong> bay leaf<span class=\"text-danger\">[ves]</span></strong></p>",
